Starstomp remembered the missile she'd taken earlier. The wounds were 
still very present, but she hoped she could still be good for a few 
rounds.

Starstomp: May I remind you, dear PunkAss, that you are way 
outnumbered and outpowered?

She jets towards him and takes her sabers out. At the last minute, she 
sees the fire coming in and dodges right, her left arm taking some 
damage. She continues and slashes twice at the dragon.
